A female AP officer was stabbed to death in Igoji, Meru county, and her riffle stolen on Wednesday morning. The unidentified officer is said to have tried to stop a robbery at Capital Sacco offices at about 9am.Chief Titus Mugambi said the attackers were non-residents.He said one was killed by an irate mob, another arrested a few kilometres away while two escaped on foot.Police said they launched investigations.